## Request Data Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant A as API Router
    participant U as Use Case
    participant R as Repository
    participant D as Database

    C->>A: HTTP Request
    A->>U: Execute command/query
    U->>R: Access data (via port)
    R->>D: SQL query
    D-->>R: Result set
    R-->>U: Domain entity
    U-->>A: DTO response
    A-->>C: HTTP Response
```
{%- if use_ai %}

## RAG Pipeline Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant API as /api/v1/ai/rag/query
    participant RAG as RAGService
    participant E as EmbeddingPort
    participant VS as VectorStorePort
{%- if use_knowledge_graph %}
    participant KG as KnowledgeGraphPort
{%- endif %}
    participant LLM as LLMPort

    C->>API: POST {question, top_k}
    API->>RAG: query(request)
    RAG->>E: embed(question)
    E-->>RAG: vector
    RAG->>VS: search(vector, top_k)
    VS-->>RAG: chunks[]
{%- if use_knowledge_graph %}
    RAG->>KG: query_triplets(question)
    KG-->>RAG: triplets[]
{%- endif %}
    RAG->>LLM: complete(question + context)
    LLM-->>RAG: answer
    RAG-->>API: {answer, sources}
    API-->>C: 200 OK
```
{%- endif %}
{%- if use_agents %}

## Agent Execution Flow

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph "Agent Runner"
        GOAL[Goal] --> PLAN[Plan]
        PLAN --> EXEC[Execute Tool]
        EXEC --> OBS[Observe Result]
        OBS -->|Loop| PLAN
        OBS -->|Done| ANS[Answer]
    end

    subgraph "Workflow Engine (LangGraph)"
        WG[Goal] --> ROUTER[Router]
        ROUTER --> PLANNER[Planner Agent]
        PLANNER --> EXECUTOR[Executor Agent]
        EXECUTOR --> REVIEWER[Reviewer Agent]
        REVIEWER -->|Needs revision| ROUTER
        REVIEWER -->|Approved| FINAL[Final Answer]
        ROUTER -.->|Checkpoint| CP[(Checkpointer)]
    end
```
{%- endif %}
